# {{obsolete|intransitive}} To speak or write in a brief manner. {{defdate|Late 16<sup>th</sup> century.}}<ref name=SOED/>
# {{transitive}} To make [[short]]er; to [[shorten]]; to [[abridge]]; to shorten by ending sooner than planned. {{defdate|First attested around 1350 to 1470.}}<ref name=SOED/>
